<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>Slogan contast</h1>
<h2>Win a new bicycle!!!</h2>
<p>We need a new slogan for our BoulderBikeTour. So we ask YOU to help us!</p>
<p>Submit here your slogan idea, first name, last name and email and you can win a brand new bicycle!</p>
<br><button class="actions"><%= link_to 'Add a new slogan', new_slogan_path %></button>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Slogan</th>
      <th>Name</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @slogans.each do |slogan| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= slogan.slogan %></td>
        <td><%= slogan.first_name %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
